  "tarball_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/ZalithLauncher/ZalithLauncher2/tarball/2.2.4",
  "zipball_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/ZalithLauncher/ZalithLauncher2/zipball/2.2.4",
  "body": "## Updates:\r\n- Synced translations from the [Weblate project](https://hosted.weblate.org/projects/zalithlauncher2/)\r\n- Added support for loading native library plugins, plugin repository: [NativeLibPlugin](https://github.com/ZalithLauncher/NativeLibPlugin/releases)\r\n- Controls: added support for using a stylus to interact with the game view\r\n\r\n## Changes:\r\n- Modpack installation: users can now cancel when entering the version name\r\n\r\n## Refactors:\r\n- Rewrote the account management screen using Hilt and MVI architecture. by [youfeng](https://github.com/youfeng11)\r\n\r\n## Fixes:\r\n- LWJGL: fixed inability to interact with Axiom mod GUI (imgui-java)\r\n- Fixed path formatting issues in the in-game file browser\r\n- Background: reduced frequent launcher background reloads\r\n- Resolution: fully fixed mouse offset issues on some devices"
